---
title: Parmesan Herb-Crusted Salmon with Garlic Mashed Potatoes, Asparagus & Creamy Mustard Sauce
description: What’s better than tender, flaky fish with a crunchy topping? How about salmon fillets coated with tangy, sharp Dijon mustard, then crusted in a mixture of Parmesan, panko, and fresh herbs? The topping toasts up nice and crisp in the oven as the fish cooks to juicy perfection. As if that weren’t enough to sell you, on the side, we’re also serving up garlic mashed potatoes and tender-crisp roasted asparagus. Weeknight luxury is just 35 minutes away!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/parmesan-herb-crusted-salmon-31d59851.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/parmesan-herb-crusted-salmon-63333166a8c43ae88c0704d8-4d050ebc.pdf
servings: 2
cuisine: North America
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/parmesan-herb-crusted-salmon-63333166a8c43ae88c0704d8
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
